## Vision

The InfraDev team initiative is part of our FY22-Q2 OKR to [implement at least 1 reliability improvement each month](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/-/issues/11396).

The team is formed of [volunteers from any of the Fulfillment teams](https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/fulfillment-meta/-/issues/206) that dedicate a small percentage of the time to the initiative.

